data.description: Discover comfortable living at its finest in this 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo located in a secure, guard-gated community. Step into a world of luxury and comfort, with a spacious open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen. The kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances that make cooking a breeze. Step outside onto your private balcony and soak in a perfect morning coffee or evening relaxation. With a 2-car attached garage, your vehicles are not only protected but easily accessible. This condo offers not just a home, but a lifestyle – one that combines convenience, security, and modern elegance. Don't miss your chance to make it yours!
